Steps on how to run the project:
1. First you need to clone the repository and pull the code in your IDE. 
2. You need to have Maven installed and configured on your PC.
3. You need to open the project in your IDE.
4. Build the project with: mvn clean install, which will run also the tests. If you would like to skip the test use: mvn clean install -DskipTests=true
5. After successful build, you can access the project on : http://localhost:8181/
6. You will see the Admin Panel with some counters for Registered PCs, Employees, PCs(which are assgned) & Employees with more then 3 PCs registered for them.
